<%= provide(:title, "#{@revision.company.name}'s Business Plan")%>

<body style="width:2500px;">

<div style="position:absolute;float:left;left:3%;font-size:35px;font-family:serif;padding-top:1cm;">
  <strong><em>The Business Model Canvas for Revision <%= @revision.id %></strong></em>
</div>

<div style="position:absolute;float:left;left:3%;width:350px;padding-top:2.6cm;">
  <span style="font-size:30px;font-family:serif;"><strong><em>Key Partners</em></strong><%= image_tag("keypartners.png", :style=> "padding-left:3cm;" )%></span><br/><br/>
  <p style="font-size:12px;color:#999;line-height:110%;">  
  Who are our Key Partners?<br/>
  Who are our Key suppliers?<br/> 
  Which Key Resources are we acquiring from partners?<br/>
  Which Key Activities do partners perform?<br/>
  </p>
  <span style="font-size:18px;font-family:serif;line-height:110%;"> 
  <%= @revision.key_partners %> 
  </span>
</div>


<div style="position:relative;float:left;left:120%;width:250px;">
  <span style="font-size:18px;font-family:serif;"><strong><em>Key Activities</em></strong><%= image_tag("keyactivities.png" , :style=> "padding-left:0.8cm;")%></span><br/><br/>
  <p style="font-size:10px;color:#999;line-height:110%;">  
  What Key Activities do our Value Propositions require?<br/>
  Our Distribution Channels?<br/> 
  Customer Relationships?<br/>
  Revenue streams?<br/>
  </p>
  <span style="font-size:14px;font-family:serif;line-height:110%;"> 
  <%= @revision.key_activities %> 
  </span>
</div>


<div style="position:relative;float:left;">
  <span style="font-size:18px;font-family:serif;"><strong><em>Value Propositions</em></strong><%= image_tag("valuepropositions.png")%></span><br/><br/>
  <p style="font-size:10px;color:#999;line-height:110%;">  
  What value do we deliver to the customer?<br/>
  Which one of our customer's problems are we helping to solve?<br/> 
  What bundles of products and services are we offering to each Customer Segment?<br/>
  Which customer needs are we satisfying?<br/>
  </p>
  <span style="font-size:14px;font-family:serif;line-height:130%;"> 
  <%= @revision.value_proposition %> 
  </span>
</div>


  

<div style="position:absolute;float:left;width:250px;">
<span style="font-size:18px;font-family:serif;"><strong><em>Customer Relationships</em></strong><%= image_tag("customerrelationships.png")%></span><br/><br/>
 <p style="font-size:10px;color:#999;line-height:110%;">  
  What type of relationships does each of our Customer Segments expect us to establish and maintain with them?<br/>
  Which ones have we established?<br/> 
  How are they integrated with the rest of our business model?<br/>
  How costly are they?<br/>
 </p>
  <span style="font-size:14px;font-family:serif;line-height:130%;"> 
   <%= @revision.customer_relationships %> 
  </span>
</div>


<div style="position:relative;float:left;left:120%;width:250px;">
<span style="font-size:18px;font-family:serif;"><strong><em>Customer Segments</em></strong><%= image_tag("customersegments.png" , :style=> "padding-left:1cm;")%></span><br/><br/>
 <p style="font-size:10px;color:#999;line-height:110%;">  
  For whom are we creating value?<br/>
  Who are our most important customers?<br/> 
 </p>
  <span style="font-size:14px;font-family:serif;line-height:130%;"> 
   <%= @revision.customer_segments %> 
  </span>
</div>



<div style="position:relative;float:left;left:120%;width:200px;">
<span style="font-size:18px;font-family:serif;"><strong><em>Key Resources</em></strong><%= image_tag("keyresources.png" , :style=> "padding-left:1cm;")%></span><br/><br/>
 <p style="font-size:10px;color:#999;line-height:110%;">  
  What key resources do our Value Propositions require?<br/>
  Our Distribution Channels? Customer Relationships?<br/> 
  Revenue Streams?<br/> 
 </p>
  <span style="font-size:14px;font-family:serif;line-height:130%;"> 
   <%= @revision.key_resources %> 
  </span>
</div>
</div>


<div style="position:relative;float:left;left:120%;width:200px;">
<span style="font-size:18px;font-family:serif;"><strong><em>Channels</em></strong><%= image_tag("channels.png" , :style=> "padding-left:1cm;")%></span><br/><br/>
 <p style="font-size:10px;color:#999;line-height:110%;">  
  For whom are we creating value?<br/>
  Who are our most important customers?<br/> 
 </p>
  <span style="font-size:14px;font-family:serif;line-height:130%;"> 
  <%= @revision.channels %> 
  </span>
</div>
</div>



<div style="position:relative;float:left;left:120%;width:200px;">
<span style="font-size:18px;font-family:serif;"><strong><em>Revenue Streams</em></strong><%= image_tag("revenuestreams.png" , :style=> "padding-left:1cm;")%></span><br/><br/>
 <p style="font-size:10px;color:#999;line-height:110%;">  
  For what value are our customers really willing to pay?<br/>
  For what do they currently pay?<br/> 
  How are they currently paying?<br/> 
  How would they prefer to pay?<br/> 
  How much does each Revenue Stream contribute to overall revenues?<br/> 
 </p>
  <span style="font-size:14px;font-family:serif;line-height:130%;"> 
  <%= @revision.revenue_streams %> 
  </span>
</div>
</div>

<div style="position:relative;float:left;left:120%;width:200px;">
<span style="font-size:18px;font-family:serif;"><strong><em>Cost Structure</em></strong><%= image_tag("coststructure.png" , :style=> "padding-left:1cm;")%></span><br/><br/>
 <p style="font-size:10px;color:#999;line-height:110%;">  
  What are the most imporant costs inherent in our business model?<br/>
  Which Key Resources are most expensive?<br/> 
  Which Key Activities are most expensive?<br/> 
 </p>
  <span style="font-size:14px;font-family:serif;line-height:130%;"> 
  <%= @revision.cost_structure %> 
  </span>
</div>
</div>







<h1> See older Revisions </h1>

<% @revision.company.revisions.each_with_index do |rev, i|  %>
<%= link_to "Revision #{i+1}", rev %> <% if rev.id == @revision.id %> (Currently viewing this) <% end %>
<% end %>

